sentences: Sachika Misawa (三澤 紗千香, Misawa Sachika, born January 13, 1993) is a Japanese voice actress and singer from Yamanashi Prefecture who is affiliated with Stardust Promotion.
Misawa began her voice acting career after winning the "Kadokawa×Up-Front Style Idol Seiyū Audition 2008" competition in February 2009.
